snippet.title: C418 - ARIA MATH | a cover
snippet.description:
Aria Math is a song by Daniel Rosenfeld (C418) that originally comes from Minecraft - a game that built many of my dearest childhood memories, as I'm sure it did yours too.

Huge thank you to Logan for letting me borrow his steel drum - it made this track!  Also huge thanks to Ellie for getting me the Stylophone featured at the end for Christmas - seriously the most fun gift ever.  And thank you to my parents for getting me the thumb kalimba that was also featured in this track!  Basically putting all of my new Christmas presents to good use here, haha. 😉

Let me know in the comments if you'd like to see any more video game covers!
